.. -*- rst -*-

Redis-LevelDB
============================================================

Dependencies
------------------------------------------------------------
1. libev:

wget http://dist.schmorp.de/libev/libev-4.11.tar.gz
tar vfxz libev-4.11.tar.gz
cd libev-4.11
./configure [--prefix=/usr/local]
make
make install

2. gmp:
   http://gmplib.org/

3. leveldb:

git clone git@github.com:appwilldev/redis-leveldb.git
cd redis-leveldb
git submodule init
git submodule update

Install
------------------------------------------------------------

[LIBEV=LIBEV_PREFIX GMP=GMP_PREFIX] make
./redis-leveldb -h

    
